75
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,159
Haotian.

76
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,440
I had my doubts,

77
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:52,240
but I was more afraid they would expose you,

78
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:52,960
so...

79
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,000
It's okay,

80
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,960
