81
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,120
Grandma.

82
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:12,040
Hello?

83
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,650
Grandma.

84
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:30,640
Grandmother.

85
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:31,920
We're back.

86
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:34,840
Grandmother.

87
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,400
Ruoyun,

88
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,600
