89
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,040
I know.

90
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,159
Grandmother.

91
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,240
Grandmother,

92
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,680
I've figured out what happened.

93
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:49,480
I wasn't asking you.

94
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:52,360
Ruoyun,

95
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:55,570
you are now a daughter-in-law of the Long family.

96
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,880
How could you act

97
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,520
with such poor judgment?

98
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,920
Your every move

99
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,720
affects the reputation of the Long family,

100
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,050
do you understand that?

101
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,120
In this city,

102
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:09,130
so many people are waiting for our family to fall,

103
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:11,360
eager to laugh at our misfortune.

104
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,800
And what do you do?

105
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,560
One single photo

106
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,970
has ruined Haotian's reputation.

107
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:21,240
As a daughter-in-law of the Long family,

108
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,900
is this how you should behave?

109
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,600
I'm sorry, Grandmother.

110
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:32,570
Please punish me as you see fit.

111
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:33,880
Ruoyun,

112
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,240
punish you?

113
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,610
What good would that do now?

114
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:38,600
Do you realize

115
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:42,640
how much damage this incident has caused to the Long Corporation?

116
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,240
Our stock prices are falling.

117
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,640
Reputation is declining

118
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,600
what should we

119
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:47,760
do about this?

120
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,360
Grandmother.

121
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:52,159
Ruoyun was actually framed by Zhao Zi'ang

122
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:54,040
I've already asked the PR department to handle it

123
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,440
and I'll find Zhao Zi'ang

124
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:58,380
to make him publicly clarify and apologize online.

125
00:07:58,760 --> 00:07:59,680
Ruoyun

126
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,000
remember this,

127
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,090
the Long family and Haotian

128
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:05,800
cannot have any stain on their reputation.

129
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:07,760
Although the Long family

130
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:09,420
isn't afraid of such matters,

131
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,720
we cannot allow others

132
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,000
to casually defame

133
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,840
our family's reputation.

134
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:20,000
I understand, Grandmother.

135
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,640
I will be more

136
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,260
careful in the future.

137
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,520
Since Haotian

138
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:29,600
has already started handling this matter,

139
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:30,960
I won't

140
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:32,659
say much more about it.

141
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:34,320
If we don't

142
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:36,039
teach you a lesson,

143
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,039
I'm afraid you might

144
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:40,289
make an even bigger mess in the future.

145
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,919
I understand what you mean, Grandmother,

146
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:44,450
