160
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:43,160
I don't care what your relationship is.

161
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:45,360
I came here today mainly for two things.

162
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,080
First,

163
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,760
stay away from Chu Ruoyun.

164
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,160
She's pure and kind-hearted,

165
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:51,890
and I don't want her to get hurt.

166
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:52,560
Second,

167
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,620
delete all the photos you posted online.

168
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,360
And

169
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,760
apologize online,

170
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:58,400
clarify

171
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:00,560
